---
// src/pages/pottery-classes-near-nashville.astro
import BaseLayout from '@layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Best Pottery Painting Classes Near Nashville, TN"
  description="Looking for pottery painting or candle making classes near Nashville? Made @ The Local Place in Centerville, TN offers unique creative experiences just 45 minutes south of Nashville. Perfect for date nights, families, and team building."
  keywords="pottery classes near Nashville, pottery painting Nashville area, candle making classes near Nashville, creative classes Nashville, art studio near Nashville"
>
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="hero-content">
      <h1>Pottery & Candle Making Near Nashville</h1>
      <p>Worth the 45-Minute Drive for Unforgettable Creative Experiences</p>
      <a href="/" class="hero-cta">Book Your Experience</a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="container py-4">
    <section class="location-intro">
      <h2>Worth the 45-Minute Drive from Nashville</h2>
      <p>
        Tired of the typical Nashville date night or family outing? Drive 45 minutes south to Centerville and find something completely different—a relaxed, owner-led pottery and candle studio where you'll actually make something with your own hands, no experience needed.
      </p>
      <p>
        This isn't a one-time craft activity. It's a real creative escape where you leave feeling like you actually created something, and the coffee's damn good too.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="location-content">
      <div class="content-grid">
        <div class="content-block">
          <h3>Easy Drive from Nashville</h3>
          <p><strong>Distance:</strong> 45 minutes south</p>
          <p><strong>Route:</strong> I-65 South → US-31E South → Centerville</p>
          <p><strong>Parking:</strong> Free parking available at 111 South Public Square</p>
          <p>
            Our studio is conveniently located on the second floor with elevator access, making it easy for visitors from Nashville, Franklin, Brentwood, and Dickson County to enjoy a quick getaway.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="content-block">
          <h3>Perfect for Nashville Visitors</h3>
          <ul>
            <li><strong>Date Nights:</strong> Romantic pottery painting with wine (BYOB)</li>
            <li><strong>Family Outings:</strong> Multi-generational creative fun</li>
            <li><strong>Team Building:</strong> Corporate groups and friend gatherings</li>
            <li><strong>Friend Visits:</strong> Unique alternative to typical Nashville activities</li>
            <li><strong>Special Celebrations:</strong> Birthdays, anniversaries, reunions</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="content-block">
          <h3>What Nashville Visitors Love</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>Intimate, welcoming studio atmosphere</li>
            <li>Owner-led experiences by Concetta</li>
            <li>No pottery experience required</li>
            <li>Professional kiln-firing and glazing included</li>
            <li>Integrated cafe with specialty coffee and snacks</li>
            <li>Flexible, judgment-free creative environment</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="content-block">
          <h3>Services Available</h3>
          <p><strong>Pottery Painting:</strong> 9 unique experiences from $5-30</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Paint Your Own Pottery Session</li>
            <li>Sip & Paint Pottery (BYOB)</li>
            <li>Holiday Ornament Painting</li>
            <li>Hand-Painted Mug Creation</li>
            <li>Ceramic Painting Workshops</li>
          </ul>

          <p style="margin-top: 1.5rem;"><strong>Candle Making:</strong> 8 unique classes from $15-25</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Pour Your Own Candle Class</li>
            <li>Custom Scent Candle Creation</li>
            <li>Eco-Friendly Candle Workshop</li>
            <li>Adult Candle-Making Night</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="testimonials">
      <h2>Why Nashville People Make the Drive</h2>
      <div class="testimonial-cards">
        <div class="testimonial-card">
          <p>"We painted matching mugs and now we use them every morning. The whole drive felt worth it the second we saw how good they looked after firing. Way better than another night in Broadway."</p>
          <p><strong>- James & Stephanie (Nashville)</strong></p>
        </div>
        <div class="testimonial-card">
          <p>"My kids are still talking about it. They each painted a plate, Concetta helped them get the colors right, and now those plates are their favorite. Makes me want to bring them back next month."</p>
          <p><strong>- The Martinez Family (Franklin, TN)</strong></p>
        </div>
        <div class="testimonial-card">
          <p>"We booked our whole team for an afternoon. Everyone walked out with a piece they made—and people actually took photos of it. Way better team bonding than trust falls."</p>
          <p><strong>- Kyle, Marketing Director (Nashville)</strong></p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="faq-section">
      <h2>Questions About Visiting from Nashville?</h2>
      <div class="faq-items">
        <details class="faq-item">
          <summary class="faq-question">
            <span>How long is the drive from Nashville?</span>
            <span class="toggle-icon">+</span>
          </summary>
          <div class="faq-answer">
            <p>
              Approximately 45 minutes south of Nashville. From downtown Nashville, take I-65 South and exit onto US-31E South toward Centerville. Our studio is located at 111 South Public Square, Upstairs.
            </p>
          </div>
        </details>

        <details class="faq-item">
          <summary class="faq-question">
            <span>Is it worth the drive?</span>
            <span class="toggle-icon">+</span>
          </summary>
          <div class="faq-answer">
            <p>
              Yeah. You'll paint something you actually like, go home with it, and use it. That's not typical for a night out.
            </p>
          </div>
        </details>

        <details class="faq-item">
          <summary class="faq-question">
            <span>Do I need to book in advance?</span>
            <span class="toggle-icon">+</span>
          </summary>
          <div class="faq-answer">
            <p>
              We recommend booking in advance, especially for groups and weekends. However, we welcome walk-ins during our business hours (Mon-Sat, 11 AM - 7 PM). Call (931) 729-8459 or email made@thelocalplacetn.com to check availability.
            </p>
          </div>
        </details>

        <details class="faq-item">
          <summary class="faq-question">
            <span>What's included in the pottery painting experience?</span>
            <span class="toggle-icon">+</span>
          </summary>
          <div class="faq-answer">
            <p>
              Everything! Our prices include pre-made pottery pieces to paint from, professional ceramic paints, brushes, aprons, glazing, professional kiln-firing, and your seat in the studio. There are no hidden fees or sitting charges. Pricing starts at just $5 per piece.
            </p>
          </div>
        </details>

        <details class="faq-item">
          <summary class="faq-question">
            <span>Can we bring our own beverages for BYOB pottery?</span>
            <span class="toggle-icon">+</span>
          </summary>
          <div class="faq-answer">
            <p>
              Yes! Our Sip and Paint Pottery experience is BYOB (Bring Your Own Beverage). You can bring wine, beer, cocktails, coffee, or any beverage you enjoy. Just let us know when you book.
            </p>
          </div>
        </details>

        <details class="faq-item">
          <summary class="faq-question">
            <span>Are group rates available for Nashville area groups?</span>
            <span class="toggle-icon">+</span>
          </summary>
          <div class="faq-answer">
            <p>
              Yes! Groups of 6 or more receive special group rates. We host corporate team building, friend groups, family reunions, and more. Contact us at (931) 729-8459 or made@thelocalplacetn.com to customize your group experience.
            </p>
          </div>
        </details>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="cta-section">
      <h2>Ready for a Creative Escape from Nashville?</h2>
      <p>
        Book your pottery painting or candle making experience today. Whether you're from Nashville, Franklin, Brentwood, or anywhere in Middle Tennessee, we're ready to welcome you!
      </p>
      <div style="text-align: center; margin-top: 2rem; gap: 1rem; display: flex; justify-content: center; flex-wrap: wrap;">
        <a href="/" class="cta-button">Book Now</a>
        <a href="tel:(931)729-8459" class="cta-button">Call (931) 729-8459</a>
        <a href="mailto:made@thelocalplacetn.com" class="cta-button">Email Us</a>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .hero {
    background: linear-gradient(rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5), rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5)), url('/hero-bg.jpg');
    background-size: cover;
    background-position: center;
    padding: 6rem 2rem;
    text-align: center;
    color: white;
  }

  .hero-content h1 {
    font-size: 3rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    color: white;
  }

  .hero-content p {
    font-size: 1.3rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .hero-cta {
    display: inline-block;
    background-color: var(--brown);
    color: white;
    padding: 1rem 2rem;
    border-radius: 4px;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 600;
    transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
  }

  .hero-cta:hover {
    background-color: var(--red);
  }

  .location-intro {
    background: var(--light-gray);
    padding: 2rem;
    border-radius: 8px;
    margin: 3rem 0;
  }

  .location-intro h2 {
    color: var(--brown);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .location-intro p {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .content-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
    margin: 3rem 0;
  }

  .content-block {
    background: white;
    padding: 2rem;
    border-radius: 8px;
    border-left: 4px solid var(--brown);
    box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
  }

  .content-block h3 {
    color: var(--brown);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    font-size: 1.3rem;
  }

  .content-block p {
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  .content-block ul {
    margin: 1rem 0;
    padding-left: 2rem;
  }

  .content-block li {
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .testimonials {
    margin: 4rem 0;
  }

  .testimonials h2 {
    color: var(--brown);
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .testimonial-cards {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
  }

  .testimonial-card {
    background: var(--cream);
    padding: 2rem;
    border-radius: 8px;
    border-left: 4px solid var(--brown);
  }

  .testimonial-card p {
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  .testimonial-card p strong {
    color: var(--brown);
  }

  .faq-section {
    margin: 4rem 0;
  }

  .faq-section h2 {
    color: var(--brown);
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .faq-items {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  .faq-item {
    border: 1px solid #ddd;
    border-radius: 8px;
    overflow: hidden;
    background: white;
  }

  .faq-question {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    cursor: pointer;
    background: var(--light-gray);
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--dark);
    user-select: none;
  }

  .faq-question:hover {
    background: #efefef;
  }

  .toggle-icon {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    transition: transform 0.3s ease;
  }

  .faq-item[open] .toggle-icon {
    transform: rotate(45deg);
  }

  .faq-answer {
    padding: 1.5rem;
    border-top: 1px solid #ddd;
  }

  .faq-answer p {
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .cta-section {
    background: var(--light-gray);
    padding: 3rem 2rem;
    border-radius: 8px;
    text-align: center;
    margin: 4rem 0;
  }

  .cta-section h2 {
    color: var(--brown);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .cta-section p {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .cta-button {
    display: inline-block;
    background-color: var(--brown);
    color: white;
    padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 4px;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 600;
    transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
  }

  .cta-button:hover {
    background-color: var(--red);
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .hero-content h1 {
      font-size: 2rem;
    }

    .hero-content p {
      font-size: 1rem;
    }

    .content-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
